{"tid":748130,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]Digimon ReArise(12) 究極體都比人秒","createTime":"2018-07-19T03:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T04:20:08.000Z","uid":40189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de7b154d834753fb2d96d59633f82d143a9ee935","tid":748130,"uid":40189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如有問題，請詳細閱讀以下資料再發問</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/154228_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F154228_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dcfa0042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/154520_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F154520_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ff885aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感人機率<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/164533_d204f039704844e176cd801198931990.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F164533_d204f039704844e176cd801198931990.png&h=5edd8d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲官網：<a href=\"https://digi-rearise.bn-ent.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigi-rearise.bn-ent.net%2F&d=5yHp%2FArRmvewwdqCqKTArNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d290d539\" target=\"_blank\">https://digi-rearise.bn-ent.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n日文資料網:<br />\n<a href=\"https://digimonrearise.boom-app.wiki/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigimonrearise.boom-app.wiki%2F&d=5yHp%2FArRmvewwdqCqKTArNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4e364434\" target=\"_blank\">https://digimonrearise.boom-app.wiki/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://gamewith.jp/digimon-rearise/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.jp%2Fdigimon-rearise%2F&d=5yHp%2FArRmvewwdqCqKTArNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ab6e805a\" target=\"_blank\">https://gamewith.jp/digimon-rearise/</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲模式:<br />\n1. 主線:每個任有3個特殊條件，達成之後有粒星星，每章主線集齊齊所有星星有額外石拎<br />\n2. 時限の渦:打bit、特訓料、食物<br />\n3. 激突戰:<br />\n自己/朋友/公會成員打主線/時限の渦會隨機出現，會跌進化料、CB medal，得分越高越易拎高級素材<br />\n己知獎勵表上嘅嘢9lv或以下都唔係必出<br />\n7lv或以上參興都有超進化core<br />\n你完成自己發現嘅lv越多，激突戰嘅lv就會升級<br />\n4. Battle Park: 即係pvp，得auto，冇得手動出技，有石同BP medal<br />\n5. Underworld: 有20層，每個任打完都有唔同獎勵<br />\n<br />\nデジモン(Digimon)介面<br />\n1. 組隊               2. 揀寵入個島入面<br />\n3. 轉友情必殺    4. 睇自己有咩寵<br />\n5. 圖鑑               6. 賣寵<br />\n<br />\n餵嘢食嘅重要性:<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餵全隊寵食嘢食到絕好調會有3個額外Drop</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.好似會影響digimon某D數值，例如肚餓爆擊率會低D<br />\n<br />\n育成:<br />\n1. 強化:即係升lv，要用bit<br />\n2. 特訓/突破界限:集齊6個特訓材料就可以提高最高等級上限<br />\n3. 進化:友情度、等級到達要求再加進化料就可以進<br />\n4. 升技:一共9lv， 可以食最終進化或前2階嘅自己升技<br />\ne.g. 飛行V龍可以食2次自己，3次V龍，4次V仔<br />\n<br />\nプラグイン(Plugin):<br />\n幅圖好似CD咁嘅物體，可以幫digimon加數值同異常狀態抗性<br />\n有得食其他plugin升到+5，再用bit upgrade星數<br />\n<br />\nガチャ:有4部抽強機，1部石抽digimon、2部石抽plugin、1部友情抽plugin<br />\n<br />\nショップ(Shop):<br />\n1.唔好買110體力包，有10電同1key，多數唔會用到key住，直接用110石回11次體好過，<br />\n2.有粒40石禁藥，餵比digimon食可以加好多親密<br />\n<br />\n傷害計算:(未確定)<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"java\">(PWR or TEC) x (1 + 隊伍中該能力最高嘅1個主動/被動BUFF - 敵人DEBUFF)*1.5 - 敵人DEF</code></pre><br />\n***1.5=爆擊傷害加成"},{"pid":"be773399e4008b39bfc9e5a46293a5c57b81b02b","tid":748130,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:39:55.000Z","msg":"有無會有空位可以收留小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a490d186741b7f0b3f0d94726b0aefd7e92f7b2","tid":748130,"uid":60083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"兩個post 12<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/748094/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/748094/page/1</a>"}]}